msgstr "Mauna Linux <dev@maunalinux.top>"

#: ui/MainWindow.glade:1013
msgid "Submit"
msgstr "Enviar"

#: ui/MainWindow.glade:1039
msgid ""
"The information shared will only be used for hardware compatibility "
"statistics and to be able to troubleshoot compatibility issues in advance.\n"
"\n"
"No personal data is collected.\n"
"\n"
"Hardware information is not shared with third parties and is only sent once "
"during this process."
msgstr ""
"La información compartida solo se utilizará para estadísticas de "
"compatibilidad de hardware y para poder solucionar problemas de "
"compatibilidad de manera anticipada.\n"
"\n"
"No se recopilan datos personales.\n"
"\n"
"La información del hardware no se comparte con terceros y solo se envía una "
"vez durante este proceso."

#: ui/MainWindow.glade:1068
msgid "Below is the data which will be sent:"
msgstr "A continuación se muestran los datos que serán enviados:"

#: ui/MainWindow.glade:1141
msgid "Copy Report"
msgstr "Copiar informe"

#: ui/MainWindow.glade:1157
msgid "Send"
msgstr "Enviar"

#: ui/MainWindow.glade:1229
msgid "System Report has been copied to your clipboard!"
msgstr "¡El informe del sistema se ha copiado en tu portapapeles!"

